This topic describes how to install the Kubernetes Command Line Interface (kubectl).

To install kubectl, follow the procedures for your operating system to download kubectl from [Pivotal Network](https://network.pivotal.io/products/pivotal-container-service). Binaries are only provided for 64-bit architectures.


