<div id="Mac" class="tabcontent" style="display: none">
 <p><ol><li>Navigate to <a href="https://network.pivotal.io/">Pivotal Network</a> and log in.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Pivotal Container Service (PKS)</strong>.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>Kubectl CLIs</strong>.</li>
  <li>Click <strong>kubectl CLI - Mac</strong> to download the kubectl binary.</li>
  <li>Rename the downloaded binary to `kubectl`.</li>
  <li>On the command line, run the following command to make the kubectl binary executable: 
    <pre class="terminal">$ chmod +x kubectl</pre></li>
  <li>Move the binary into your <code>PATH</code>. For example:
    <pre class="terminal">$ mv pks /usr/local/bin/kubectl</pre></li>
 </p>
